218409171.text: The fact that p16 (INK4A) and flavopiridol negate Cdk4 mediated suppression of yeast cell growth implies that this simple system can be used as a screen for identifying Cdk4 specific antagonists which may mimic p16 (INK4A) in the cancer cell cycle.
